    <item>
      <title>Shopify 因强劲的销售增长前景而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/shopify-reports-third-quarter-revenue-that-beat-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shopify Inc. 表示将在假日购物季保持快速销售增长，随后股价飙升，表明这家加拿大电子商务公司吸引大型企业的策略正在取得成效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/shopify-reports-third-quarter-revenue-that-beat-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 12:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>购物需求推动 Sea 股价上涨，利润上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/sea-tops-profit-estimates-after-fending-off-tiktok-lazada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其电子商务业务报告其首次实现调整后盈利后，Sea 有限公司的股价出现了一年半多以来的最大涨幅，这表明该公司在印度尼西亚等东南亚市场上与规模更大的中国竞争对手保持着一定地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/sea-tops-profit-estimates-after-fending-off-tiktok-lazada</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政策和宏观经济威胁下，中国科技股需要盈利提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/china-tech-stocks-need-earnings-boost-amid-trump-macro-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于国内宏观前景不明朗以及地缘政治风险上升，中国科技股迅速降温，投资者正期待本周将公布的主要企业盈利报告，以期带来新的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/china-tech-stocks-need-earnings-boost-amid-trump-macro-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 00:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
